<i>adverb</i>: 삐 [삐] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>삐 [삐]</dt><br>
<dd>1. beep</dd><br>
<dd>벨이나 호출기 등이 울릴 때 나는 소리.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating the sound of a bell, beeper, etc., ringing.</dd><br>
<dd>2. whistling</dd><br>
<dd>호루라기나 피리 등을 불 때 나는 소리.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating the sound made by a whistle, pipe, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. with a harsh cry</dd><br>
<dd>어린아이가 듣기 싫게 우는 소리.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating the sound of a child crying gratingly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>